    "media_with_dynamic_text_qNLAkC": {
      "type": "media-with-dynamic-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_9depYL": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Quality, Not Quantity",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_h1": false
          }
        },
        "text_8YiAEG": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Even as demand grew, we refused to become a warehouse brand that just “shipped boxes.”</p><p>We kept our assembly team in-house. We trained each new joiner personally. We built partnerships with UK suppliers — some just down the road — so we could control quality and support local economies.</p><p>We made a decision: if something wasn’t right, we’d fix it. No questions. No long waits. Just a real person, on the phone, ready to help. That’s still our promise today.</p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_9depYL",
        "text_8YiAEG"
      ],
      "name": "Media with dynamic text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled_design_3.png",
        "layout": "left",
        "image_fit": "contain",
        "media_width": 50,
        "media_scale": 100,
        "text_align": "text-start",
        "color_scheme": "none"
      }
    },
    "image_banner_LRtC7X": {
      "type": "image-banner",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Rnp8rW": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Pandemic Years: A True Test",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_h1": false
          }
        },
        "text_pNKJN4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When COVID hit, the world paused. But people still needed beds. They needed them more than ever — for comfort, for home offices, for kids growing faster than expected.</p><p>We worked with a skeleton crew and kept operations safe. We took thousands of calls from customers stuck at home. We adapted quickly, launching new delivery options, sourcing additional fabrics when supply chains failed, and expanding our online support.</p><p>It wasn’t easy. But it reminded us why we exist: to bring comfort, quality, and honesty into people’s homes.</p>",
            "enlarge_text": true
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_Rnp8rW",
        "text_pNKJN4"
      ],
      "name": "Image banner",
      "settings": {
        "image_desktop": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled_design_11_f48557a5-11d5-46c2-a2b3-618052ea1452.png",
