    "rich_text_AJFNrX": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_G8TUp6": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What Bedroom King Means Today",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "heading_h1": false
          }
        },
        "text_bR3fbY": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We’re no longer just a Yorkshire startup, but we still think like one. We still obsess over feedback. We still test every new model. We still argue (in a good way!) over fabric shades and drawer depth.</p><p>We’ve helped thousands of people across the UK get a better night’s sleep, make more space in their homes, and feel good about where they spend one-third of their lives.</p><p>And we’re not done yet.</p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_G8TUp6",
