    "multi_column_Y7ajNV": {
      "type": "multi-column",
      "blocks": {
        "column_aPEhBQ": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "enable_media": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Panel-Storage-Bed-Ottoman.png",
            "media_scale": 80,
            "heading": "Ottoman Beds",
            "text": "<p>Our ottoman beds are the best-selling models for a reason. In modern UK homes where space is tight and storage is precious, our lift-up ottoman frames offer a practical and beautiful solution.</p><p>Each gas-lift mechanism is reinforced to support daily use. Customers often ask: “Will this last for years?” Our answer is simple — yes, because we build them to.</p><p>Instead of thin particleboard bases, we use solid wood or reinforced boards. We also offer both front-lift and side slider designs, depending on room layout.</p><p><strong>Popular finishes:</strong></p><ul><li>Plush Velvet in silver, steel, and mink</li><li>Naples Fabric for a matt, clean look</li><li>Crushed Velvet for customers who want glamour</li></ul><p>Every ottoman is made to order, allowing you to choose the size, headboard, and finish that best suits your home.</p>",
            "button_label": "Ottoman Beds",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/king-size-bed-with-storage"
          }
        },
        "column_x6CbxY": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "enable_media": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Panel-Cream-Divan-Bed_1.webp",
            "media_scale": 80,
            "heading": "Divan Bed",
            "text": "<p>Divan bases are classic for a reason. Ours features durable timber frames, optional drawers, and solid platform tops. Unlike flatpack bases from budget brands, Bedroom King divans come pre-built in sections for easier delivery and longer life.</p><p><strong>Why people love them:</strong></p><ul><li>Great for guest rooms and smaller spaces</li><li>Optional storage drawers that don’t compromise design</li><li>Compatible with all Bedroom King headboards</li></ul><p>These are the workhorses of our range—simple, stylish, and built to last.</p>",
            "button_label": "Divan Bed",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/3ft-single-divan-bed-frame"
          }
        },
        "column_VJMCkV": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "enable_media": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Oversized-Headboard-Bedframe-Grey.png",
            "media_scale": 80,
            "heading": "Custom Headboards",
            "text": "<p>A headboard should be more than an afterthought. Ours are designed as statement pieces, whether you're looking for subtle elegance or bold luxury.</p><p><strong>Choose from:</strong></p><ul><li>Panelled headboards</li><li>Wingback designs</li><li>Button-tufted Chesterfield style</li><li>Horizontal lines for a modern look</li></ul><p>Height, fabric, and design are all customisable. You can even request samples to match your wall paint or bedding.</p>",
            "button_label": "Custom Headboards",
            "button_link": "https://www.bedroomking.co.uk/products/replacement-headboard-split-headboard-only"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
