            "heading": "Sophie & Mark from Birmingham",
            "text": "<p>“We downsized last year and were worried about storage. The bedroom King’s ottoman bed in silver plush has honestly transformed our space. It’s comfortable, solid, and so spacious underneath. Delivery was quick, and the guys even helped move our old bed out.”<br/><br/></p>",
