            "heading": "Harpreet from Leicester",
            "text": "<p>“The build quality is next-level. You can feel it in the base when you sit. And their customer service? Best I’ve had in years. I changed my mind about the fabric, and they sorted it with no fuss.”</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_YLpdnH": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "enable_media": false,
            "media_scale": 100,
            "heading": "Rachel from Brighton",
            "text": "<p>“I run an Airbnb and needed something stylish but hard-wearing. Their divan base with a wingback headboard gets compliments in almost every review. It’s been 18 months and still looks brand new.”</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
      },
