    "media_with_text_FG3EXg": {
      "type": "media-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_acakr7": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Collaborations & Community",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_h1": false
          }
        },
        "text_qdMgbx": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We’re proud of our British roots, and that pride extends into how we give back and collaborate.</p><p>In 2023, we partnered with a local shelter initiative in West Yorkshire to donate 50 beds and mattresses to housing support programs. These weren’t clearance items—they were custom-built for comfort and dignity.</p><p><strong>We’ve also collaborated with:</strong></p><ul><li>Independent interior designers to curate headboard trends for our seasonal collections.</li><li>Local upholsterers in Sheffield to train apprentices in traditional techniques.</li><li>British textile innovators to test new eco-conscious fabrics, like recycled polyester blends and plant-dyed linens.</li></ul><p>These partnerships help us stay connected to the community and stay ahead of sustainable trends.</p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_acakr7",
        "text_qdMgbx"
      ],
      "name": "Media with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled_design_14.png",
        "video_external": "",
