    },
    "image_banner_7Kn8Nd": {
      "type": "image-banner",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_fCc94X": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where We’re Headed Next",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_h1": false
          }
        },
        "text_nAWfhp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As we grow, our mission remains the same: build better beds, honestly.</p><p><strong>Why Bedroom King Is Built to Last</strong></p><p>In a market saturated with fast furniture and fleeting trends, Bedroom King stands for longevity—in our builds, our service, and our values.</p><p>We aren’t trying to sell the most beds. We’re trying to sell the ones that matter most to you. Whether that’s a chic velvet frame for your first home, a sturdy divan for the kids’ room, or a custom piece for an unusual layout, our team is ready to build it with care.</p><p>We listen. We adapt. We evolve. And we do it all without losing sight of the Yorkshire workshop where it began.</p><p>Because at the end of the day, we’re not just in the business of beds. We’re in the business of better sleep, better homes, and better choices.</p><p>From our family to yours—thank you for making Bedroom King part of your story.</p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
